description:
The 85SouthShow hosts DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller, and Clayton English are back this time in Phoenix at Stand Up Live! With their WildNOut style of comedy they have the whole place cracking up! Recorded Live they discuss the heatwave, Floyd Mayweather, single women, sex, and more!!
